general.gigTitle: be your front end and backend website developer

sellerCard.description: Hi, I'm Khateeb, a web developer with 7 years experience in Website development, Webdevelopment and android applications. I can create modern & responsive web sites/applications with high quality and professional look. As every website/application that represents a business plays a very important role in its growth. That's why I treat every website according to its nature.

description.content:
Before start the order !

Please Text ME to discuss the project details.


I am offering my services as a front end developer and web designer. I have 4+ years of experience in building mid to large scale websites and web applications based on Web standard technologies. I worked for so many clients with positive feedback and have good relations with them. Please share your project I will assist you accordingly.


For Web design, I use Adobe XD, Figma, Adobe Illustrator, or Sketch.

For front end web development, I use HTML5, CSS3, Bootstrap, Javascript, ReactJS, and Jquery.

For Back end web development, I prefer to use PHP or NODE-JS.

For Database integration in website, I use MySql.

I have also worked as a PSD to HTML specialist (Front end web developer).

  •  HTML5
  • CSS3
  • Bootstrap 3 & 4
  •  Mobile App Design
  • Sass
  • Materialize CSS
  • jQuery
  • PSD to HTML
  • PSD to Wordpress
  • Xd to Html
  • Responsive Templates
  • Pixel Perfect Design
  • Clean Code
  • Custom Fonts
  • Adobe XD

** 100% Money Back Guarantee **


Why me?

- 100% REFUND If youre unhappy with my work

- Quality Work

- 24/7 Availability

- 100% Customer Satisfaction Guaranteed

- Flexible Timing

- Reasonable Cost

- Fast Delivery

Kindly Contact before Order
